ken bucket (`policy.reprocess.rate-limit-per-second`, default 100)\n\n**Key Methods:**\n```java\n@Scheduled(fixedDelayString = \"${policy.reprocess.scan-interval-ms:30000}\")\npublic void scanAndReprocessInitEntities()\n\n@Async(\"policyReprocessListenerExecutor\")\n@EventListener\npublic void onPolicyReprocessRequested(PolicyReprocessRequestedEvent event)\n\nprivate void triggerScan(String triggerSource)  // Acquires global lock\nprivate void drainInitEntities()                // Query + batch process\nprivate void processBatchConcurrently(List<Long> batchIds, ReprocessRateLimiter rateLimiter)\nprivate void reprocessOneEntity(Long entityId, ReprocessRateLimiter rateLimiter)\nprivate void resetEntityProcessingState(Entity e)\n```\n\n**Metrics Tracked:**\n- `policy_reprocess_mark_init_last_failed_batches` (gauge)\n- `policy_reprocess_mark_init_run_seconds` (timer, tagged by result)\n- `policy_reproc_lock_acquire_total` (counter, by lock name and result)\n- `policy_reprocess_scan_lock_consecutive_failures` (gauge)\n- `policy_reproc_lock_hold_seconds` (timer, by lock name)\n- `policy_reprocess_entity_completed_total` (counter, by result)\n- `policy_reprocess_rate_limiter_wait_total` (counter)\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Database Repository Methods**\n**File:** `/private/tmp/temper-arch/A/ingestion/src/main/java/com/fortinet/nac/ingestion/repository/EntityRepository.java`\n\n**Reprocess-Related Queries:**\n```java\n// Find entities that need marking (not already INIT)\nList<Long> findTopNIdsNeedMarkForReprocess(\n    Long lastId, ReprocessState targetState, Pageable pageable);\n\n// Batch mark entities for reprocessing\nint markBatchForReprocess(List<Long> ids, ReprocessState targetState);\n\n// Find top N by state\nList<Long> findTopNIdsByReprocessState(ReprocessState state, Pageable pageable);\n\n// Lightweight projection for lock info\nOptional<EntityProcessLockInfo> findProcessLockInfoById(Long id);\n\n// Atomic claim: INIT -> RUNNING (only succeeds if currently INIT)\nint claimInitEntityForReprocess(Long id, Instant updatedAt);\n\n// Update reprocess state by id\nint updateReprocessStateById(Long id, ReprocessState state, Instant updatedAt);\n```\n\n---\n\n### 8. **DTOs for Reprocess Flow**\n\n**MarkForReprocessResult:**\n```java\nint updatedCount;      // Total entities marked\nint failedBatches;     // Number of failed batch updates\nint failedCount;       // Total entities in failed batches\n```\n\n**MarkForReprocessResponse:**\n```java\nint markedCount;       // Successfully marked count\nint failedBatches;     // Failed batch count\nint failedCount;       // Failed entity count\nlong timeCostMs;       // Execution time\nString status;         // FAILED | PARTIAL_SUCCESS | SUCCESS\nString message;        // Human-readable message\n```\n\n**EntityQueryDTO (for querying failed entities):**\n```java\nString stage;          // Filter by processingStage\nInteger code;          // Filter by processingCode\nInteger pageNum;       // Default 1\nInteger pageSize;      // Default 10\nString sortKey;        // createdAt | processingStage | type\nString sortOrder;      // asc | desc\n```\n\n**EntityStateDisplayDTO (for display-status endpoint):**\n```java\nLong id;\nString type;\nString hostIdentity;\nString userIdentity;\nString processingStage;\nInteger processingCode;\nInstant updatedAt;\nString displayStatus;  // init | running | enforced | failed | unknown\n```\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Configuration Properties**\nFrom `EntityServiceImpl` and `PolicyReprocessJob`:\n```properties\npolicy.reprocess.mark-init-batch-size=1000          # Batch size for marking\npolicy.reprocess.scan-batch-size=100               # Query batch size\npolicy.reprocess.max-candidates-per-scan=1000      # Max entities per scan run\npolicy.reprocess.rate-limit-per-second=100         # Rate limiter\npolicy.reprocess.scan-lock-ttl-seconds=900         # Distributed lock TTL\npolicy.reprocess.scan-interval-ms=30000            # Scheduled job interval\n```\n\n---\n\n### 10. **T